overview: Experience Neal McCoy like you've never seen hi before... LIVE! and in HD with 5.1 Dolby Digital. This special edition DVD features over 60 minutes of the two-time Entertainer of the Year performing at the 2005 HODAG Country Music Festival in Rhinelander, Wisconsin. John Neal and 33,000 of his closest friends for a roof-rattling, beer blasting, country rockin' good time.
title: Neal McCoy: Live!
